<title><![CDATA[Bucatini Amatriciana]]></title>
<description><![CDATA[This is tradidionally made with guaciale, a kind of bacon made with pig's cheeks, and bucatini, which are very thick spaghettli-like tubes. Substitute as required. The name comes fron a town in the county of Rieti, Amatrice.]]></description>
