<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[if using canned tomatoes start making the sauce, otherwise you can leave it until the pasta is cooking]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[cube the guanciale, and sautÃ¨ in oil with chilli powder until browned, 1 m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add the wine, cook until reduced]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[if using canned tomatoes: add them, break with a fork, add salt to taste and cook for 15 m on low heat]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[bring a large pot of salted water to boil, then cook the bucatini (or other pasta) in them]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[if using passata, add passata, and salt to taste, cook 5 m on low heat]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[cook the pasta until al dente, drain and toss in the sauce pot]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add pecorino to the pot, mix throughly, serve]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
